---
const facts = [
  { value: "2", label: "bestsellery wydawnicze" },
  { value: "100k+", label: "odbiorców" },
  { value: "viral", label: "marketing oparty na emocjach" },
];
---

<section class="py-28 lg:py-40 border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute -left-40 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 font-display font-semibold text-[20rem] text-white/[0.025] select-none pointer-events-none whitespace-nowrap">
    BESTSELLERS
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-6">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-acid">04 — Wydawnictwo</div>
        <h2 class="mt-6 font-display font-semibold text-bone text-5xl lg:text-7xl">
          Tworzymy<br />
          historie, które<br />
          <span class="text-acid">sprzedają<br />się same.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-bone/70 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Nie tylko generujemy zasięgi — budujemy emocje i narracje, które przyciągają uwagę mas. Nasze projekty wydawnicze osiągnęły status bestsellerów.
        </p>

        <dl class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
          {facts.map((f) => (
            <div>
              <dt class="font-display font-semibold text-acid text-3xl lg:text-4xl">{f.value}</dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-bone/60">{f.label}</dd>
            </div>
          ))}
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 lg:gap-8">
        {[
          {
            cover: "/books/rybak-cover.jpg",
            title: "Zbigniew Rybak.",
            sub: "Syn Józefa",
            href: "https://www.zbigniewrybak.pl",
            offset: "lg:translate-y-6",
          },
          {
            cover: "/books/rozal-cover.jpg",
            title: "Rozal.",
            sub: "Instrukcja samodestrukcji",
            href: "https://www.ksiazkarozala.pl",
            offset: "lg:-translate-y-6",
          },
        ].map((book, i) => (
          <a
            href={book.href}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class={`group block transition-transform duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 ${book.offset}`}
          >
            <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
              <img
                src={book.cover}
                alt={`Okładka książki ${book.title} ${book.sub}`}
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.04]"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-5 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-bone/40 mb-2">
                  Bestseller · 0{i + 1}
                </div>
                <div class="font-display font-semibold text-bone text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-none">
                  {book.title}
                </div>
                <div class="mt-2 text-bone/55 text-sm lg:text-base">
                  {book.sub}
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-acid text-xl shrink-0 mt-1 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                ↗
              </span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-bone/50 italic text-lg">
        „To samo podejście wykorzystujemy w kampaniach dla marek."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
